data.description:
Welcome to Hidden Lakes, a convenient yet hidden gem off Highway 17. This charming single-story ranch is a haven of comfort and style. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by the heart of the home- a warm and welcoming great room. The crackling fireplace invites you to unwind in the evenings, creating a cozy ambiance that pairs perfectly with the vaulted ceilings, giving the space an airy and expansive feel.
As you move through this home, your feet will appreciate the smooth, all-laminate flooring that unifies the entire living space. The kitchen is a chef's delight, boasting plenty of cabinets for storage, solid granite countertops, and all-stainless appliances that gleam with modern sophistication. Adjacent to the kitchen, a delightful breakfast area lets you start your day with backyard views through the sliding doors.
The master suite is a secluded retreat featuring a spacious two-person bathroom and a walk-in closet that fulfills your storage dreams. Two additional bedrooms, tucked away on the opposite side of the house, share a guest bath conveniently located in between. Granite countertops adorn the kitchen and all bathrooms, adding a touch of luxury to everyday living.
Natural light floods the interior through large windows, creating a bright and cheerful atmosphere. Step outside, and you'll discover a large private backyard, fully fenced for your peace of mind—the perfect space for entertaining and gardening. Everything has its place in the garage, with built-in cabinets ensuring organization. The outdoor well takes care of the irrigation needs, making the landscaping a breeze to maintain. This home also comes equipped with a water-softening system.
In Hidden Lakes, this residence offers a house and a lifestyle where every detail has been thoughtfully designed to make you feel right at home. Welcome to a life of comfort, style, and tranquility.
